channel.description:
If anyone knows...this maybe over some/most of you.
[code] NpcDefinition:@147ee05 Walk:@15b9e68 Mask:@1fcf0ce Definition:@1256ea2 [/code]
The only part really important to me is either the NpcDefinition or the Walk, I am trying to decipher this into a value for the emote of the npc. Not sure if this is against the rules, but rep if you help in any way.
If it helps anyone I'm printing a hash which I know is a horrible thing, but I'm trying to convert it into a string...
